# NAME: Trading_Apps
# AUTHOR: Kevin (kevshen13)
# REPO: https://github.com/kevshen13/surge-rules
# DESCRIPTION: Trading applications rule list for Surge
# UPDATED: 2026-04-04
# MAINTENANCE: Maintain this list by trading software and platform usage.
# RULE: Include charting, execution, order-flow, and analytics platforms that should follow the Trade Platform group.
# RULE: Keep broker-specific account, auth, and gateway domains in broker-specific lists instead.
# NOTE: thinkorswim / Schwab and IBKR stay in us-brokers.list rather than this app list.

